00:01:21.978 --> 00:01:26.918
IN HER HOME IN PETACH TIKVA, ISRAEL. TODAY IS APRIL THE THIRD

00:01:26.918 --> 00:01:31.628
NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN, AND THE LANGUAGE WILL BE YIDDISH MIXED WITH HEBREW.

00:01:33.330 --> 00:01:34.454
SHALOM.

00:01:34.714 --> 00:01:36.862
kenst undz zogn day-

00:01:36.862 --> 00:01:38.235
dayn nomen, bite?

00:01:38.005 --> 00:01:38.842
JA.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:40.411
Vayner SOFIA.

00:01:40.570 --> 00:01:42.251
un vi alt bistu?

00:01:44.903 --> 00:01:45.950
dray un akhtsik.

00:01:45.950 --> 00:01:47.888
fun, heyst dos, mer

00:01:48.653 --> 00:01:49.372
yo.

00:01:49.564 --> 00:01:50.418
vifl?

00:01:50.492 --> 00:01:51.650
geb- MI?

00:01:51.353 --> 00:01:55.397
vifl a- vifl yorn hostu? vif- vi alt bistu?

00:01:55.723 --> 00:01:59.665
zek- zeks un nayntsik. zeks un akhtsik.

00:01:58.947 --> 00:02:00.606
zeks un akhtsik yor.

00:02:00.297 --> 00:02:01.033
JA.

00:02:00.606 --> 00:02:03.075
velkhe yor host geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:02.288 --> 00:02:05.201
n- EIN TAUSEND nayn hundert a- elef.

00:02:05.022 --> 00:02:06.535
in velkhe shtot?

00:02:06.017 --> 00:02:07.951
in Tshernovits, Bukovine.

00:02:07.637 --> 00:02:10.618
Tshernovits hot gevezn damolt Bukovine.

00:02:09.696 --> 00:02:11.749
damolts iz geven Bukovine, yo.

00:02:11.518 --> 00:02:13.962
kenst a bisele fartseyln fun di shtub?

00:02:13.962 --> 00:02:18.245
vi azoy hot gevezn di lebn in Tshernovits, ven host geboyrn gevorn?

00:02:17.914 --> 00:02:22.464
dos lebn iz geven zeyer sheyn. iz geven ruik. men iz geven in der heym.

00:02:23.128 --> 00:02:28.454
m'hot ge- m'hot gearbet shver, ABER m'hot gehat dos AUSKOMMEN, un s'iz geven zeyer a sheyn, freylekh lebn.

00:02:28.461 --> 00:02:29.366
biz

00:02:29.490 --> 00:02:31.391
nayntsn eyn un fertsik.

00:02:31.228 --> 00:02:33.702
yo, ober vo- vos di tate hot gemakht?

00:02:33.608 --> 00:02:37.612
der tate iz geforn mit a FIAKER. damolst iz nokh nisht geven keyn AUTOBUSn.

00:02:37.612 --> 00:02:40.638
s'iz nokh nisht, iz nor geven di elektrishe ban

00:02:40.847 --> 00:02:42.022
elektrish.

00:02:41.691 --> 00:02:42.478
yo.

00:02:42.332 --> 00:02:48.260
un er iz geforn mit al- mit a, a FIAKER, un iz geforn mit ale rabonim

00:02:48.260 --> 00:02:53.711
un hot gehat, er iz geforn maynstn mit di rabon- geven der Boyaner rebe, der Kaputshinitser

00:02:53.711 --> 00:02:57.565
s'iz geven a sakh rabonim, iz er geforn mit zey, mit zeyer rabonim.

00:02:57.975 --> 00:02:59.217
un

00:02:59.612 --> 00:03:02.491
un dernokh dem iz gevorn iz t-

00:03:02.498 --> 00:03:08.145
JA, iz, hot men ge- di ershte AUTOBUSn iz er geven a shutef tsu di autobusn.

00:03:08.573 --> 00:03:13.207
azoy hobn mir gehat dos AUSKOMMEN. nisht vern raykh, ober sheyn, ruik.

00:03:13.450 --> 00:03:15.418
un vos di mame hot getun?

00:03:14.901 --> 00:03:17.054
gornisht. ikh oykh gornisht.

00:03:17.348 --> 00:03:20.053
d- froy, froyen hobn nisht gearbet

00:03:20.053 --> 00:03:21.644
zenen gezesn in shtub

00:03:21.685 --> 00:03:23.484
un geven in kekh un hobn

00:03:23.642 --> 00:03:24.918
gefirt di virtshaft.

00:03:25.161 --> 00:03:27.166
host gehat

00:03:27.166 --> 00:03:29.188
bridern, shvestern?

00:03:28.317 --> 00:03:34.485
ikh bin dos tsente kind. mayn mame iz geven zeyer a shvakhe. zi hot nisht gekent oysd- zi hot dos gehat dos ershte kind

00:03:34.485 --> 00:03:36.375
iz dos geshtorbn in tsvey yor, iz

00:03:36.375 --> 00:03:38.965
fun damolst iz zi gevorn zeyer krank, LEIGEND

00:03:38.965 --> 00:03:42.823
un hot mer ken kinder nisht gekent oystrogn, un ikh bin dos tsente kind.

00:03:43.673 --> 00:03:50.484
un kenst fartseyln a bisele vi azoy mh di yidishe lebn hot gevezn? m'hot geganen in shul

00:03:48.870 --> 00:03:52.706
dos li- dos lebn iz geven zeyer sheyn. s'iz geven ruik

00:03:52.706 --> 00:03:55.549
m'iz, yidish. m'hot opgehit shabes

00:03:55.549 --> 00:03:57.538
s'iz gekumen fraytik farnakht

00:03:57.848 --> 00:04:01.018
iz men nisht mer geforn un nisht mer gegangen

00:04:01.018 --> 00:04:02.948
un nisht mer, di GESCHAFTE farmakht

00:04:02.948 --> 00:04:04.692
un m'hot opgehit shabes.

00:04:05.442 --> 00:04:06.195
yo.

00:04:06.049 --> 00:04:09.013
gedenkst vi azoy me hot gemakht shabes in di shtub?

00:04:09.270 --> 00:04:15.088
JA, s'iz nisht geven a shabes, m'hot gebakn koyletsh, un m'hot geba- m'hot gekokht fish

00:04:15.229 --> 00:04:18.294
un m'hot gekoyft bro- un m'hot gema-

00:04:19.498 --> 00:04:20.808
UNK

00:04:21.844 --> 00:04:25.635
m'hot, m'hot gebakn broyt oyf der gantser vokh

00:04:25.658 --> 00:04:26.515
aleyn.

00:04:26.515 --> 00:04:27.676
nisht gekoyft.

00:04:28.105 --> 00:04:30.664
s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer a ruik lebn.

00:04:30.822 --> 00:04:32.166
shver.

00:04:30.822 --> 00:04:33.364
un in shul vi azoy hot gevezn?

00:04:32.475 --> 00:04:35.147
in shul iz mayn tate gevezn

00:04:35.147 --> 00:04:36.218
zeyer an

00:04:36.218 --> 00:04:37.380
UNK

00:04:37.791 --> 00:04:42.243
ayngezeener balebos. er iz geven a khosid funem Kaputshinitser rebe

00:04:42.243 --> 00:04:46.360
un s'iz geven di Kaputshinitser shul, un er iz geven gabe dort in shul.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:48.284
un zeyer bekoved

00:04:48.284 --> 00:04:50.005
nisht raykh, ober bekoved

00:04:50.005 --> 00:04:50.779
gelebt.

00:04:51.443 --> 00:04:52.179
un

00:04:52.303 --> 00:04:57.596
vi azoy hot gevezn in, in shul? gedenkst? vi azoy, v- vu hostu gelernt?

00:04:55.628 --> 00:04:56.482
v-

00:04:57.163 --> 00:05:00.380
ikh hob gelernt in der zibn yeriker UNK in der folkshul.

00:05:00.623 --> 00:05:04.144
ikh hob gemakht finef yo- finef klasn, un mer nisht.

00:05:04.302 --> 00:05:08.964
un ikh bin geven zeyer opgehit un m'hot mikh d-, vayl ikh bin geven dos tsente kind.

00:05:08.964 --> 00:05:11.433
un m'hot mikh nisht geshikt lerner keyn fakh

00:05:11.777 --> 00:05:15.380
un, un ikh, un ⟨zey hobn mikh nisht gegangen shtrengen⟩ mitn lernen.

00:05:15.380 --> 00:05:16.918
bin geven in der heym.

00:05:16.975 --> 00:05:19.196
un vos me hot gelernt in shul?

00:05:19.185 --> 00:05:24.292
un shul hot men ge- s'iz geven a rumenishe shul. m'hot gelernt rumenish helft un helft daytsh.

00:05:25.513 --> 00:05:26.216
yo.

00:05:26.172 --> 00:05:29.085
un yidish, yidishkeyt host nit gelernt?

00:05:27.673 --> 00:05:30.856
yidish iz geven eyn mol in der vokh iz gekumen a lerer

00:05:31.015 --> 00:05:34.167
a rav, un hot gelernt mit di yidishe kinder yidish

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:35.250
in shule?

00:05:34.167 --> 00:05:39.598
ikh bin, in shule, un mit di kristlekhe kinder iz geven ale, hot men zey gelernt.

00:05:39.992 --> 00:05:44.508
vayl s'iz geven a shule, a folkshule, mit yidn un mit kristn.

00:05:45.088 --> 00:05:54.076
un kenst nokh fartseyln epes fun di lebn, vi, vi azoy me peysekh oder purim epes, di yontoyvim vi azoy?

00:05:52.176 --> 00:05:55.919
JA, s'iz geven zeyer sheyn di yontoyvim zeyer opgehit.

00:05:55.919 --> 00:05:58.569
un purim hot men geshikt shalekhmones un

00:05:58.569 --> 00:06:01.419
m'hot nisht gezen, m'hot nisht gearbet, m'iz nor gegangen

00:06:01.419 --> 00:06:04.229
yeder eyner dem tsveytn hot geshikt shalekhmones.

00:06:04.229 --> 00:06:06.059
dos hot men gezen a gantsn tog.

00:06:06.059 --> 00:06:08.280
un peysekh, peysekh iz geve-

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:09.838
peysekh iz mayn tate

00:06:10.198 --> 00:06:14.228
gegangen in alte zkeynes hoyz un hot genumen a yid

00:06:14.228 --> 00:06:16.346
un hot geven bay im tsu oyrekh.

00:06:16.346 --> 00:06:21.448
un dos gantse yor iz gevezn a, a rumenisher SOLDAT, a, a zelner.

00:06:21.505 --> 00:06:26.355
vos er hot, nisht gevoynt dort un iz geven bay undz, er iz gekumen sh- oyf shab-

00:06:26.355 --> 00:06:28.105
fraytik oyf der nakht un shabes.

00:06:28.234 --> 00:06:32.805
un m'hot im geshikt peklekh fun der heym, vayl bay di rumener iz geven zeyer karg dos esn

00:06:32.811 --> 00:06:36.811
hot men im geshikt peklekh oyf undzer ADRESSE, un er hot dos bay undz gehaltn

00:06:36.811 --> 00:06:41.301
un iz geven ale yorn biz er hot oysgedint iz er geven bay undz azoy vi a eygn kind.

00:06:42.531 --> 00:06:45.782
un s'hot gevezn nokh mishpokhe in Tshernovits?

00:06:46.041 --> 00:06:51.418
mayn tate hot nisht gehat zeyer a sakh mishpokh- er hot gehat tsvey brider un a shvester in Daytshland.

00:06:51.930 --> 00:06:56.632
un er iz geblibn do, vayl do iz geven kosher. dort hot er nisht gevolt forn

00:06:56.655 --> 00:07:00.924
zey zenen geven zeyer gut situirt. zey hobn gehat geshefte fun mebl un fun ale

00:07:00.924 --> 00:07:03.964
fun radyo. zeyer, zeyer gut ⟨ge- tseshtelt⟩

00:07:03.964 --> 00:07:06.964
ABER er hot ahin nisht gevolt forn, vayl s'iz nisht geven kosher.

00:07:06.966 --> 00:07:09.829
er iz geven zeyer opgehit, ge- kosher ge-

00:07:10.324 --> 00:07:13.206
zeyer sheyn. ikh hob oykh gelernt

00:07:13.206 --> 00:07:15.836
vi azoy me darf ophitn yidishkeyt.

00:07:17.361 --> 00:07:18.063
yo.

00:07:18.694 --> 00:07:20.949
un di mame hot gehat oykhet mishpokhe?

00:07:21.090 --> 00:07:25.000
di mame hot gehat shvester un brider, zenen geven ale in Tshernovits.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.790
un ale oysgeshtorbn oyfn veg

00:07:26.790 --> 00:07:29.201
in lager arayn. keyner iz nisht geblibn.

00:07:27.857 --> 00:07:30.635
vi hot geheyst di mame? vi?

00:07:29.275 --> 00:07:30.065
vi?

00:07:30.065 --> 00:07:31.040
Pesye.

00:07:31.198 --> 00:07:32.457
un di tate?

00:07:32.216 --> 00:07:33.706
der tate Itsik.

00:07:34.253 --> 00:07:38.499
di mame hot geheysn Pesye, un geboyrn Roznblat fun der heym.

00:07:39.889 --> 00:07:42.769
zi hot gehat a groyse mishpokhe, zeyer a sheyne mishpokhe

00:07:42.769 --> 00:07:44.399
ABER zenen ale oysgeshtorbn

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:46.759
oyfn veg, far hunger un far tsores.

00:07:46.759 --> 00:07:48.405
geven zeyer a shverer veg.

00:07:49.103 --> 00:07:51.099
di rumener hobn undz aroysgeshikt

00:07:51.099 --> 00:07:55.166
ABER s- m'hot geshlogn un geharget. m'hot oysgetun. m'hot gemakht khoyzek.

00:07:55.166 --> 00:07:58.536
s'iz geven a yid mit a bord, hot im der ⟨helft⟩ bord aropgenumen

00:07:58.536 --> 00:08:01.236
m'hot zeyer, zeyer, zeyer khoyzek gemakht fun yidn.

00:08:01.337 --> 00:08:02.495
s'hot zeyer g-

00:08:02.923 --> 00:08:04.396
ikh hob geboyrn

00:08:04.396 --> 00:08:07.372
dos kley- di groyse, iz in

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:09.738
nayn un ⟨draysiker⟩ yor geboyrn

00:08:09.738 --> 00:08:13.886
un di kleyne iz geboyrn IM eyn un fertsik, IM ershtn oktober. s'iz geven yomkiper.

00:08:13.707 --> 00:08:16.198
ven host heyrat gevorn?

00:08:15.377 --> 00:08:17.666
IM akht un draysiker yor.

00:08:17.790 --> 00:08:18.881
IM

00:08:17.807 --> 00:08:18.864
un t-

00:08:19.697 --> 00:08:21.311
nayntn yener.

00:08:21.334 --> 00:08:22.998
EIN TAUSEND NEUN HUNDERT ACHT.

00:08:21.688 --> 00:08:24.213
ven host, host bakent dayn man?

00:08:24.540 --> 00:08:27.920
o, shoyn UNK a por UNK. a fir finef yor zenen mir gegangen.

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:28.584
JA.

00:08:28.540 --> 00:08:32.483
kenst fartseyln fun dem, vi azoy me hot geganen damolt, vi azoy me hot

00:08:32.860 --> 00:08:34.710
tsunoyfgekumen

00:08:33.315 --> 00:08:38.574
er iz, er, ikh hob gehat fun mayn mamen a shvester, iz zi geven in Vizhnits farheyrat.

00:08:38.918 --> 00:08:43.248
un dort hob ikh im KENNEN GELERNT in UNK in a sh- in a bod dort.

00:08:43.248 --> 00:08:44.918
m'iz gegangen shpatsirn

00:08:44.918 --> 00:08:48.088
hob ikh im dort KENNEN GELERNT., a por yor zenen mir gegangen.

00:08:48.088 --> 00:08:51.368
er hot gearbet in Tshernovits ale yon- er iz geven a shnayder

00:08:51.368 --> 00:08:53.188
hot er gearbet in Tshernovits.

00:08:53.548 --> 00:08:56.178
un undz ho'mir zikh getrofn biz

00:08:56.178 --> 00:09:00.618
biz undz ho'mir, UNK dray fir ⟨yorn⟩ zenen mir gegangen biz mir hobn khasene gehat.

00:09:00.940 --> 00:09:02.976
velkhe yor host khasene gehat?

00:09:03.555 --> 00:09:09.219
IM akht un draysiker yor, IM nayntn yener, akht, EIN TAUSEND NEUN HUNDERT ACHT UND draysik.

00:09:09.664 --> 00:09:13.033
un vi iz di nomen fun dayn man? vi heyst ir?

00:09:12.786 --> 00:09:14.585
Meyer MAKS Vayner.

00:09:14.828 --> 00:09:15.598
yo.

00:09:15.638 --> 00:09:17.944
un nokh di khasene, vos host gemakht?

00:09:17.427 --> 00:09:20.292
nokh der khasene hob ikh gevoynt mit di eltern tsuzamen

00:09:20.292 --> 00:09:24.052
vayl zey hobn mikh nisht aroysge- ikh bin dokh geven zeyer opgehit.

00:09:24.278 --> 00:09:27.714
hobn mir gevoynt tsuzamen biz IM JAHRE eyn un fertsik.

00:09:27.940 --> 00:09:33.182
eyn un fertsik hot men undz aroysgeshikt. s'iz geven der ershter oktober, iz geven yomkiper

00:09:33.407 --> 00:09:34.886
un

00:09:34.892 --> 00:09:38.422
akhtn oder tsentn oktober hot men undz aroysgeshikt fun di shtiber.

00:09:38.422 --> 00:09:40.792
zenen mir geven tsvey vokhn in a geto

00:09:40.792 --> 00:09:42.457
un dan hot men undz geshikt

00:09:42.457 --> 00:09:44.521
keyn TRANSNISTRIA in a lager.

00:09:44.646 --> 00:09:48.347
yo. o- vi az- vi azoy host gehert fun di milkhome?

00:09:48.347 --> 00:09:51.576
di milkhome hot shoyn gevezn tsvey, tsvey yor.

00:09:49.962 --> 00:09:52.072
di milkhome iz gevezn

00:09:52.072 --> 00:09:57.652
m'iz gegangen shpatsirn un m'hot gehert, me, m'hot gelezn tsaytung un m'hot gehert vos s'hot zikh getun.

00:09:57.704 --> 00:09:58.494
yo.

00:09:58.045 --> 00:10:03.456
host gekent mentshn vos hobn shoyn gevezn do, in di milkhome? zey hobn gekumen nokh Tshernovits un

00:10:03.816 --> 00:10:04.952
fartseylt

00:10:04.952 --> 00:10:05.936
epes?

00:10:05.672 --> 00:10:10.289
NE- m'hot o- NEIN, mit, ver s'iz avekgegangen iz er mer nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:10:11.258 --> 00:10:18.643
ABER m'hot geredt, m'hot gehe- m'hot geleyent tsaytung. s'iz geven, ver s'hot gehat a radyo, damolst nisht yeder hot gehat a radyo

00:10:18.717 --> 00:10:20.820
iz hot men gehert dem radyo.

00:10:22.260 --> 00:10:27.100
un kenst fartseyln di, di ershte tog ven di

00:10:27.100 --> 00:10:29.764
daytshn hobn arayngekumen in Tshernovits?

00:10:30.647 --> 00:10:32.666
vi azoy s'hot gevezn damolt?

00:10:30.681 --> 00:10:31.502
di

00:10:33.297 --> 00:10:34.770
d- di

00:10:34.770 --> 00:10:37.391
d- dos veys ikh, gedenk ikh shoyn nisht.

00:10:40.401 --> 00:10:43.939
di daytshn zenen arayngekumen. di rumener zenen antlofn.

00:10:44.603 --> 00:10:48.785
un dernokhdem zenen di daytshn avekgegan. s'iz geven a arbets batalyon

00:10:48.785 --> 00:10:51.586
zenen di rumener gekumen, un m'hot tsunoyfge- m'hot

00:10:51.586 --> 00:10:52.579
gezogt

00:10:52.905 --> 00:10:55.599
az me darf k- zikh geyn in a geto.

00:10:55.892 --> 00:10:57.978
s- ales avekgegan in geto

00:10:58.120 --> 00:11:00.943
⟨oyf hunderter⟩ hot men undz geshikt. s'iz geven transportn.

00:11:00.943 --> 00:11:02.529
hot men undz geshikt biz

00:11:03.908 --> 00:11:05.454
O- Otaki

00:11:05.460 --> 00:11:06.770
far MOGILOV.

00:11:06.962 --> 00:11:10.618
biz ahin zenen mir geforn, un fun dort zenen mir shoyn gegangen tsu fus.

00:11:10.827 --> 00:11:12.072
yo, ober

00:11:12.072 --> 00:11:15.712
i- lomir geyn tsurik nokh di ershte teg.

00:11:13.797 --> 00:11:14.618
yo.

00:11:15.535 --> 00:11:16.389
nu

00:11:15.712 --> 00:11:17.742
ven di daytshn hobn arayngekumen

00:11:17.742 --> 00:11:20.692
un m'hot kontsentrirt ale vu?

00:11:20.496 --> 00:11:24.860
ah, di, az m'hot ⟨zey⟩ genumen di gantse yugnt, un m'hot zey oysgeshosn.

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:24.202
yo.

00:11:24.917 --> 00:11:29.689
mit a mol dray hundert. s'ersht- dem ershtn tog dray hundert. di shenste yidishe kinder.

00:11:29.689 --> 00:11:32.116
tsvontsik biz finef un tsvontsik.

00:11:33.490 --> 00:11:35.559
un vu m'hot zey genumen?

00:11:35.970 --> 00:11:42.624
s'iz gevezn aza bi- ikh UNK ikh gedenk nisht vi se ge- bir palast, s'hot ge- aza groyser salo- ba- palast.

00:11:42.624 --> 00:11:46.899
un dort ahin hot men zey ale kontsentrirt, UNK aroysgekumen zenen zey shoyn nisht mer.

