shnayder iz geven zeyer a

00:22:05.076 --> 00:22:08.946
mir hobn gekent makhn par- undz ho'mir nokh gehat a bisl gelt fun der heym.

00:22:10.082 --> 00:22:12.573
un vi azoy di kinder hobn gevaksn?

00:22:13.035 --> 00:22:14.733
esn hot gevezn?

00:22:15.128 --> 00:22:19.535
s- in der fri iz gekumen et- etlekhe goyim dort in geto

00:22:19.535 --> 00:22:21.685
un m'hot gebrakht es- un m'hot gebrakht

00:22:21.685 --> 00:22:23.925
m'hot gekent koyfn, yo. vos hot men ge-

00:22:23.925 --> 00:22:26.655
m'hot gemakht a, gekoyft a tsvey kartofl, mir hobn gemakht a SUP.

00:22:26.655 --> 00:22:28.010
hot men gehat dem gantsn tog.

00:22:28.076 --> 00:22:29.105
m'hot gegesn.

00:22:29.105 --> 00:22:31.237
broyt iz nisht geven. s'iz geven

00:22:32.256 --> 00:22:34.157
m- oyf tsu iberlebn.

00:22:35.142 --> 00:22:42.201
vi azoy hot gevezn di shkheynes KSHARIM mit di, mit di goyim?

00:22:42.201 --> 00:22:43.911
vi azoy m'hot gelebt m-

00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:47.973
s'iz geven gute mentshn un s'iz geven shlekht- s'iz geven bay yidn oykh azoy, gute mentshn un shlekhte mentshn.

00:22:47.973 --> 00:22:53.393
undz ho'mir getrofn zeyer gute mentshn. mayn man shpetsyel, m'hot im shtark lib gehat vayl er iz geven a shnayder

00:22:53.393 --> 00:22:58.524
un er hot far zey geneyt f- mit gelt, on gelt, farshidn. hot men im zeye shtark lib gehat.

00:22:59.087 --> 00:23:00.971
un m'hot im zeyer a sakh geholfn.

00:23:02.057 --> 00:23:06.914
un s'hot gevezn epes yidishe lebn in di geto? in di lager?

00:23:06.833 --> 00:23:08.801
abso- gornisht.

00:23:06.914 --> 00:23:08.733
m'hot gekent

00:23:09.077 --> 00:23:10.720
absolut nisht.

00:23:10.444 --> 00:23:12.193
shabes makhn?

00:23:10.740 --> 00:23:15.782
na- m'hot zikh nisht gevust fun, di ukraynishe yidn hobn d- nish- m'hot nisht gevust.

00:23:15.782 --> 00:23:17.306
m'hot gornisht gevust.

00:23:18.291 --> 00:23:21.204
un di daytshn hobn arayngekumen dortn?

00:23:20.653 --> 00:23:23.611
s'iz gekumen yedes mol ARBEITSGRUPEN

00:23:23.611 --> 00:23:26.541
oder zenen durkhgegangen oder zenen gekumen

00:23:26.541 --> 00:23:28.951
⟨maynstmol⟩ hot zikh ongeshikert a da- daytsh

00:23:28.951 --> 00:23:31.301
un iz arayngekumen, hot geshlogn geharget.

00:23:31.369 --> 00:23:33.922
ABER m'hot teykef gerufn di rumener

00:23:33.922 --> 00:23:36.510
hobn zey, ver s'hot gevolt hot geholfn.

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:39.416
m'hot im batsolt tsu der shef geto

00:23:39.416 --> 00:23:42.240
iz geven oykh a Tshernovitser, dokter Kurland

00:23:42.287 --> 00:23:46.770
er hot tsunoyfgenumen bay di yidn nokh dos letste vos m'hot gehat

00:23:47.755 --> 00:23:51.481
un hot batsolt far di zhendarma- fun di zhendarms

00:23:51.481 --> 00:23:53.790
eynem, un yener hot undz gehi-

00:23:53.880 --> 00:23:56.264
s'iz epes geven tsores, hot men im gerufn

00:23:56.264 --> 00:23:57.420
hot er

00:23:57.420 --> 00:23:58.514
undz geholfn.

00:23:59.213 --> 00:23:59.899
yo.

00:23:59.770 --> 00:24:04.573
akhuts fun di shef geto, hobn gevezn nokh yidn vos hobn ge-

00:24:04.478 --> 00:24:06.446
yo, s'iz gevezn.

00:24:04.663 --> 00:24:06.496
UNK

00:24:06.553 --> 00:24:08.774
s'iz geven a por yidn, UNK

00:24:09.152 --> 00:24:12.220
dem shef geto hob ikh gekent vayl er iz oykh geven a Tshernovitser.

00:24:12.220 --> 00:24:14.158
ABER UNK geven zeyer a sakh.

00:24:14.215 --> 00:24:16.791
vos zey hobn geholfn UNK farshidn.

00:24:18.059 --> 00:24:22.495
un zey hobn aranzhirt di KSHARIM mit

00:24:21.454 --> 00:24:24.960
zey hobn aranzhirt ver se darf geyn oyf arbet. m'hot avekgeshikt

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:26.260
keyn

00:24:26.905 --> 00:24:29.818
Tultshin iz men mer nisht tsurikgeku- oyf arbet

00:24:30.010 --> 00:24:33.460
iz men mer nisht tsurikgeku- ver s'iz avekgegangen iz mer nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:24:33.460 --> 00:24:37.507
ober mayn man hot gehat glik. m'hot im gemakht a, a verkshtat fun shnayderay.

00:24:37.507 --> 00:24:38.526
m'hot gemakht

00:24:38.565 --> 00:24:40.376
fun shnayderay

00:24:40.376 --> 00:24:44.730
un a shuster un a f- shildn maler. dray fakh.

00:24:44.730 --> 00:24:48.195
hot men gemakht aza shtub un m'hot dos gearbet

00:24:48.302 --> 00:24:49.983
un der

00:24:50.884 --> 00:24:55.730
⟨der hot er⟩ zey kasirt, un di yidn zenen geven tsufridn, zey hobn nisht gedarft geyn oyf arbet.

00:24:56.149 --> 00:24:58.803
anfang iz er gegangen tsu der zhandarm

00:24:58.803 --> 00:25:02.670
dort putsn, roymen, hot men gut ongeshlogn. m- i-

00:25:02.670 --> 00:25:04.820
zey hobn gemakht khoyzek fun di yidn.

00:25:05.633 --> 00:25:06.403
yo.

00:25:06.645 --> 00:25:08.917
vifl yorn host gevezn dortn?

00:25:08.215 --> 00:25:09.407
dray yor.

00:25:09.227 --> 00:25:10.419
biz ven?

00:25:10.763 --> 00:25:12.596
biz in may

00:25:13.648 --> 00:25:16.156
dakht zikh may s'iz geven, undz ze'mir tsurikgekumen.

00:25:16.348 --> 00:25:23.474
zenen mir tsurikgekumen. zenen mir gegangen keyn Zhmerinke. fun STANISLAVCHYK biz keyn Zhmerinke iz geven akht kilometer.

00:25:23.474 --> 00:25:28.138
zenen mir ahingegangen, un dort hobn mir getrofn a yid vos er iz mit der ban

00:25:28.431 --> 00:25:34.736
hot er undz erloybt un hot undz arayngenumen in a vagon fun di ferd, fun di beheymes.

00:25:34.759 --> 00:25:41.134
zenen mir gera- arayngegan ale tsuzamen. di eltern zenen dokh mer nisht geven, ober ikh mit mayn man mit di kinder.

00:25:41.134 --> 00:25:43.295
un nokh geven mishpokhes fun Vizhnits

00:25:43.295 --> 00:25:49.176
ze'mir arayngegan in dem vagon. ⟨der⟩ iz geven zeyer a fayner, er hot nisht gezogt ABER m'hot gezen az er iz a yid.

00:25:49.176 --> 00:25:50.559
ze'mir geforn

00:25:50.559 --> 00:25:52.314
biz Tshernovits.

00:25:52.314 --> 00:25:54.120
ongekumen keyn Tshernovits

00:25:54.120 --> 00:25:58.040
hot men undz nisht arayngelozt. undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn pasport, nisht keyn papirn.

00:25:58.266 --> 00:26:02.785
ze'mir tsurikgegangen UNK, dos heyst a STANZION far Tshernovits.

00:26:02.785 --> 00:26:06.646
dort zenen mir geblibn biz bay nakht, iz gekumen eyner, hot er undz erloybt.

00:26:06.653 --> 00:26:08.202
undz megn mir aroysgeyn

00:26:08.202 --> 00:26:11.490
un ikh hob gehat a tante nokh, fun mayn mamen a shvester

00:26:11.631 --> 00:26:13.461
in Tshernovits

00:26:13.461 --> 00:26:16.621
ze'mir gegangen tsun ir, un zi hot undz gegebn a tsimer

00:26:16.621 --> 00:26:20.691
un dort hobn mir b- gevoynt biz tsum avekforn keyn R- yo

00:26:20.676 --> 00:26:25.074
y- ober loz mir tsurikgeyn tsu, tsu di lager.

00:26:25.350 --> 00:26:30.170
host a mol gedarft bahaltn fun di ukraynen, fun di DEUTSCHEN, fun em-

00:26:28.202 --> 00:26:32.527
yo, s'hot zikh, di, der sef geto iz gekumen, hot gezogt

00:26:32.527 --> 00:26:34.443
az di daytshn kumen arayn

00:26:34.443 --> 00:26:38.136
men vet undz hargenen. ver, dos, yeder zol antloyfn.

00:26:37.855 --> 00:26:40.228
ven iz dos gevezn? velkhe yor?

00:26:40.302 --> 00:26:41.325
gedenkst?

00:26:43.322 --> 00:26:48.525
do- ho'mir, ikh hob genumen eyn kind oyf di hent, un er dos andere, un er hot gehat

00:26:48.525 --> 00:26:50.516
fun di goyim a bakantn

00:26:50.516 --> 00:26:55.596
vos er hot dokh bay zey gearbet, mit gelt, on gelt, abi er zol zitsn in der varem, un me zol im nisht

00:26:55.596 --> 00:26:57.671
UNK zeyer a fayner, a

00:26:57.671 --> 00:26:58.802
a shuster

00:26:58.802 --> 00:27:00.464
BOYKU.

00:27:00.464 --> 00:27:04.143
ze'mir dort geven dray tog. ikh hob damolst gehat a shvere gripe

00:27:04.143 --> 00:27:08.213
un zi di froy hot nisht gehat keyn kinder, hot zi gehaltn mayne kinder, un ⟨zi hot zikh zey⟩

00:27:08.213 --> 00:27:11.893
un ale goyim zenen ahin arayngekumen, un m'hot zikh gefreyt mit di yidn.

00:27:12.043 --> 00:27:14.214
zeyer gut hot men undz oyfgenumen.

00:27:13.528 --> 00:27:16.150
un zey hobn gevust az du bist a yidish-

00:27:14.963 --> 00:27:16.623
yo, zikher.

00:27:16.623 --> 00:27:18.593
zey hobn gevust az me kumt undz hargenen

00:27:18.593 --> 00:27:20.583
un ven me kum- me treft undz bay zey

00:27:20.583 --> 00:27:24.123
harget men zey dokh oykh. ober trots dem hot men undz gehaltn

00:27:24.123 --> 00:27:26.033
a y- a por tog zenen mir dort geven

00:27:26.033 --> 00:27:29.730
un dernokh dem iz mayn man gegangen, hot gezen az me meg shoyn tsurikkumen

00:27:29.730 --> 00:27:32.010
ze'mir tsurikgekumen bay undz in shtub

00:27:32.010 --> 00:27:34.796
un s'iz shoyn gornisht geven. m'hot ales geganvet

00:27:34.796 --> 00:27:37.918
dos benkl mit ⟨alemen ho'mir⟩ shoyn, ho'mir gehat dort

00:27:37.918 --> 00:27:40.770
ze'mir dortn geblibn biz tsum avekforn.

00:27:40.815 --> 00:27:43.070
un ven host avekgeforn?

00:27:42.942 --> 00:27:43.915
fun dort?

00:27:43.633 --> 00:27:44.437
yo.

00:27:46.485 --> 00:27:48.844
gedenk nisht UNK s'iz geven may, shaynt mir.

00:27:48.844 --> 00:27:50.192
d- nokh dray yor.

00:27:50.991 --> 00:27:52.051
di

00:27:52.051 --> 00:27:54.022
di rusn hobn arayngekumen?

00:27:55.345 --> 00:27:59.610
yo. du rusn zenen, di rumener zenen antlofn, un di rusn zenen arayngekumen.

00:28:00.795 --> 00:28:01.897
un ven

00:28:01.897 --> 00:28:05.751
vi azoy host gevust az du kenst shoyn tsurikkumen, ts- tsurikforn?

00:28:06.482 --> 00:28:09.912
di, di, di, zey hobn undz gezogt, fun der, fun di

00:28:09.912 --> 00:28:12.792
di OFFIZIERE fun der, fun der GENDARMERIE.

00:28:13.232 --> 00:28:18.119
zeyer, mayn man hot far zey geneyt, zey hobn undz zeyer lib gehat. hot gekent redn mit zey, rumener

00:28:18.666 --> 00:28:23.115
hobn zey gezogt "kukt, s'iz shoyn bafrayt. undz geyen mir avek, ir kent shoyn avekf- aheymforn."

00:28:23.712 --> 00:28:26.473
zenen mir azoy aheymgekumen. MANCHE zen-

00:28:25.112 --> 00:28:28.244
un du gedenkst velkhe yor dos iz gevezn?

00:28:35.676 --> 00:28:36.699
shat nisht

00:28:36.857 --> 00:28:37.441
gedenk nisht

00:28:39.878 --> 00:28:45.966
ikh veys undz ze'mir geven tsvey a halb yor in, in Tshernovits nokh, un dan ze'mir tsurikg- avekgeforn keyn UNK.

00:28:45.966 --> 00:28:46.942
RUMANIEN.

00:28:48.248 --> 00:28:49.375
OKAY.

00:28:49.375 --> 00:28:53.035
 vi, vi azoy hot gevezn forn tsurik?

00:28:53.310 --> 00:28:54.080
vu?

00:28:54.188 --> 00:28:54.994
nokh

00:28:54.994 --> 00:28:56.308
nokh Tshernovits?

00:28:57.023 --> 00:29:02.166
nokh Tshernovits zenen mir geforn mit der ban. m'hot undz genumen, zenen mir gelegn oyf der erd me zol undz ⟨nisht zen⟩

00:29:02.166 --> 00:29:03.111
keyner

00:29:03.111 --> 00:29:05.117
un di kinder zenen geven ruik

00:29:05.140 --> 00:29:07.817
un, azoy zenen mir geforn biz keyn Tshernovits.

00:29:08.093 --> 00:29:11.760
MANCHE zenen gegangen tsu fus, ABER undz ze'mir nisht gan, undz ho'mir gehat glik.

00:29:11.760 --> 00:29:13.532
m'hot getrofn a zeyer a faynem

00:29:14.725 --> 00:29:17.081
ofitsir fun der, fun der ban.

00:29:24.445 --> 00:29:26.854
ven hostu gekumen nokh Tshernovits

00:29:26.854 --> 00:29:28.640
host getrofn mishpokhe?

00:29:29.220 --> 00:29:32.575
fun mayn mamen a shvester. zi iz, zi iz nisht geven in lager.

00:29:32.575 --> 00:29:33.736
zi hob ikh getrofn.

00:29:33.793 --> 00:29:37.553
ABER vayter iz geven ales oys- dort vu ikh hob gevoynt dray

00:29:37.553 --> 00:29:39.650
dray gasn loyter yidn.

00:29:39.650 --> 00:29:42.480
keyner nisht geve- ikh hob gekent tsurikgeyn in mayn shtub

00:29:42.480 --> 00:29:44.476
ABER ikh hob moyre gehat tsu geyn ahin

00:29:44.476 --> 00:29:47.116
vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn eyntsike, ales oysgeshtorbn.

00:29:47.665 --> 00:29:51.743
dray gasn, ales, nisht eyn mentsh iz geblibn.

00:29:53.115 --> 00:29:55.053
un dayn man's mishpokhe?

00:29:56.119 --> 00:30:00.534
man's mishpokhe iz oykhet oys- zenen oysgeshtorbn, ABER zey zenen

00:30:01.030 --> 00:30:03.524
MANCHE zenen gegangen tsurik in Vizhnits

00:30:03.524 --> 00:30:06.480
azoy iz UNK. undz ho'mir nisht gehat keyn shum mishpokhe.
